emergency
---------

* create log file in /tmp first, after install, move the log file to install dir: /var/log/install.log

* fix color in dash and sh

	printf "%b" "\e[1;31mThis is red text\e[0m"
	printf '%b' "\033[32;1mpassed\033[0m\n"

* /bin/mv will generate dangling link in the below case:

	mkdir -p a/b
	cd a/b
	touch a
	ln -s a b
	mv b ../

then b is a dangling link, fix this by wrapper the mv up with function:

	mv() {
		if [ -L b ]; then
			ln -s "$(readlink -e "${src}")" "${dst}"
		else
			command mv "${src}" "${dst}"
		fi
	}

